author: Martin Driensky
name: Chata pod Rysmi
aditionalPersons: Katarína Jesenská - manželka, Elemíra Jesenská - svokra
reasonForReturn: Here, I focus on a range of items and features that we use in life without giving them a second thought such as Coca Cola, body muscles and holding ones own breath. Though, most of these notes are not fundamentally necessary, they are such that you can use them for a good laugh, at a drinks party or for picking up women or men.stops the functioning of the heart for a very tiny second.
